sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM vehicles_conditions 
WHERE condition_id = 1;

SELECT AVG(price) AS average_price
FROM vehicles
WHERE date_listed >= '2023-01-01';

SELECT price
FROM vehicles
WHERE transmission = (SELECT transmission_id FROM transmissions WHERE transmission_name = 'Manual');

external_knowledge:
Four-wheel drive (4WD) refers to a system in which power is transmitted to all four wheels of a vehicle; 
 A truck is a type of vehicle with an open topped body and typically used for carrying goods or materials; 
 The average price of a vehicle make and model is the total price of all vehicles of that make and model divided by the number of vehicles, excluding those with a zero or negative price.
